{"type": "article", "id": 7267, "title": "Eggpicnic 砖土时钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-11T07:22:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234247VNbRA42pXSwJl9mg.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是 Eggpicnic 推出的一款时钟，采用城市拆迁时的废弃建材制造。他们认为，建筑是城市的灵魂，而废弃建筑物材料中包含着城市的灵魂，用这些材料制作时钟，有着凝固时间的隐喻。这个时钟分三层，最下面一层底盘采用的是拆迁剩下的红砖，将红砖打碎成粉，与生物树脂结合制成。而上面的两层分别代表时针和分针的转盘，均由竹木制成。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234244gW3025PMcILxuBUy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342449OPDuzord2MwhUIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234245X2ROKnSNkfwFMhZJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234245UF4ZyA6rKJ3CekWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234246PU3jZSE517zMDAqu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}